\keepn \f12 \fs22 \f12 \cf5 \fs36 \b \i [10] Tips\par \cf1 \fs22 \b0 \i0 \pard \f12 \fs24 \pard \cf0 This section includes tips on how to use the WinDEU level editor, and a sub-section about the limits of Doom/Windeu.\par \par See:\par \tab \uldb Editing tips\uldb0 \v EDITING_TIPS\v0 \par \tab \uldb Doom / WinDEU limits\uldb0 \v DOOM_LIMITS\v0 \par \f10 \par \page
